oral correlated noise may be a\nbeneficial resource for efficient transport in large scale quantum networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Nov 2017 04:47:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 Jul 2018 11:32:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-26"}
