ness results in the even\n$L^p$-Minkowski problem, as well as improved stability estimates in the\nBrunn-Minkowski and anisotropic isoperimetric inequalities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Nov 2017 10:05:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Nov 2017 13:44:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 20 Feb 2018 20:31:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-22"}
