ely, detect. Finally, disc fragmentation is\nshown to be an efficient manufacturer of free floating planetary mass objects,\nand the typical multiplicity of systems formed via gravitational instability\nwill be low.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Nov 2017 12:51:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Nov 2017 10:14:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-10"}
